llm_outputs.rationale: The table on page 153 specifies the maximum lot coverage for the Medium Industrial (MI) district as 'None [1]'. The footnote [1] indicates that development within the WPO is subject to built-upon limits in another section, but this doesn't apply to the general MI district. Therefore, there is no maximum lot coverage specified for MI.
